OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of wet and rather breezy
OL,6,Fweather will feed eastwards across the
OL,7,Fregion this morning. Patchy lighter
OL,8,Frain will linger in the east this
OL,9,Fafternoon, whilst sunnier skies arrive
OL,10,Fin the west, and the breeze will ease
OL,11,Ftoo.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering rain soon
OL,14,Fclearing in the east, leaving a dry
OL,15,Fnight with clear spells. The breeze
OL,16,Fwill fall light allowing a few fog
OL,17,Fpatches to form, and staying frost-
OL,18,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
