OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FApart from an isolated light
OL,6,Fshower, Saturday promises to be a dry
OL,7,Fday with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,8,FFeeling fresher in the gentle
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly wind, though pleasant in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FAfter a
OL,13,Fchilly start both Sunday and Monday
OL,14,Flook dry with light winds and some
OL,15,Fsunshine. A cooler northeasterly wind
OL,16,Fon Tuesday giving more cloud and the
OL,17,Fodd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
